CustomField.description: If checked, a responder’s identity is not associated with the responder’s response record. Note that when explicit survey assignments are created, a responder’s identity is attached to the responder’s response record.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Enable to not associate a participants' identify with a survey response records. Note that when explicit survey assignments are created, a participants' identity is attached to the participants' survey response records.
CustomField.label: Dep Anonymize Responses
